#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "The \"{NAME_APP}\" mobile application and web service are developed and operated by Vadym Bezsmertnyi, FOP (\"us\", \"we\", or \"our\"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you access and use our Telegram bot management platform and services (\"Service\")."
msgstr "The \"{NAME_APP}\" mobile application and web service are developed and operated by Vadym Bezsmertnyi, FOP (\"us\", \"we\", or \"our\"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you access and use our Telegram bot management platform and services (\"Service\")."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Information We Collect"
msgstr "Information We Collect"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Information Collection"
msgstr "Information Collection"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "We collect information to ensure the effective functionality of the {NAME_APP} service. The data collected may include:"
msgstr "We collect information to ensure the effective functionality of the {NAME_APP} service. The data collected may include:"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Telegram account information: username, user ID, and profile data."
msgstr "Telegram account information: username, user ID, and profile data."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Group and channel data: information about Telegram groups you manage."
msgstr "Group and channel data: information about Telegram groups you manage."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Member data: information about group members for management purposes."
msgstr "Member data: information about group members for management purposes."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Message templates: custom templates you create for automated messaging."
msgstr "Message templates: custom templates you create for automated messaging."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Analytics data: usage statistics and performance metrics."
msgstr "Analytics data: usage statistics and performance metrics."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Subscription information: for managing your account and processing payments."
msgstr "Subscription information: for managing your account and processing payments."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Device information: for app functionality and security."
msgstr "Device information: for app functionality and security."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Use of Information"
msgstr "Use of Information"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "We process your data based on legitimate interests and contractual necessity. The collected data is used to:"
msgstr "We process your data based on legitimate interests and contractual necessity. The collected data is used to:"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Provide Telegram group management functionality."
msgstr "Provide Telegram group management functionality."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Analyze group activity and member statistics."
msgstr "Analyze group activity and member statistics."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Send automated messages and notifications through your bot."
msgstr "Send automated messages and notifications through your bot."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Manage message templates and bot settings."
msgstr "Manage message templates and bot settings."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Process subscriptions and billing."
msgstr "Process subscriptions and billing."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Improve service functionality and user experience."
msgstr "Improve service functionality and user experience."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Telegram API Integration"
msgstr "Telegram API Integration"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Our service integrates with Telegram's API to provide group management features. We only access data that you authorize through Telegram's authentication process. The {NAME_APP} service requires the following permissions:"
msgstr "Our service integrates with Telegram's API to provide group management features. We only access data that you authorize through Telegram's authentication process. The {NAME_APP} service requires the following permissions:"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Read group information: to display group details and member lists."
msgstr "Read group information: to display group details and member lists."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Send messages: to deliver automated notifications and templates."
msgstr "Send messages: to deliver automated notifications and templates."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Manage groups: to perform administrative tasks you authorize."
msgstr "Manage groups: to perform administrative tasks you authorize."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Access member data: to provide member management features."
msgstr "Access member data: to provide member management features."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Analytics data: to provide usage statistics and insights."
msgstr "Analytics data: to provide usage statistics and insights."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Data Security"
msgstr "Data Security"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Your data is protected using industry-standard security measures. We implement the following security practices:"
msgstr "Your data is protected using industry-standard security measures. We implement the following security practices:"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Sharing Information with Third Parties"
msgstr "Sharing Information with Third Parties"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "We may share your data with third parties in the following cases:"
msgstr "We may share your data with third parties in the following cases:"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "International Data Transfers"
msgstr "International Data Transfers"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Your data may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data in accordance with applicable data protection laws."
msgstr "Your data may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data in accordance with applicable data protection laws."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "User Rights"
msgstr "User Rights"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "To exercise your rights, contact us at {CONTACT_EMAIL}. You have the following rights:"
msgstr "To exercise your rights, contact us at {CONTACT_EMAIL}. You have the following rights:"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Access your data: You can review the data we store about you."
msgstr "Access your data: You can review the data we store about you."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Delete your data: You can request the deletion of your information."
msgstr "Delete your data: You can request the deletion of your information."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Revoke Telegram permissions: You can disconnect your Telegram account at any time."
msgstr "Revoke Telegram permissions: You can disconnect your Telegram account at any time."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Export your data: You can request a copy of your data in a portable format."
msgstr "Export your data: You can request a copy of your data in a portable format."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Rectify your data: You can request correction of inaccurate personal data."
msgstr "Rectify your data: You can request correction of inaccurate personal data."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Restrict processing: You can request limitation of data processing under certain circumstances."
msgstr "Restrict processing: You can request limitation of data processing under certain circumstances."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Data Retention"
msgstr "Data Retention"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide our services. Data is automatically deleted when you delete your account or revoke Telegram permissions. Some data may be retained for legal or security purposes as required by law. We comply with applicable data protection laws including GDPR where applicable."
msgstr "We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide our services. Data is automatically deleted when you delete your account or revoke Telegram permissions. Some data may be retained for legal or security purposes as required by law. We comply with applicable data protection laws including GDPR where applicable."

