msgid "The service processes Telegram group data for management purposes. Users are responsible for ensuring they have the necessary permissions to manage the groups they connect to the service. {NAME_APP} is not liable for any data loss or unauthorized access to Telegram groups. Users must comply with Telegram's Terms of Service and API usage policies."
